Motormaster smiles at the view of the prisoner falling, he cocked his gun,
and readied to move in. Then he heard the Decepticon distress signal, as
would the other crew members. "Switchblade, Bodicons, move in on the
Maximal, but dont destroy him. Stratus, come with me." Motormaster lands on
the ground, and Transforms into his truck mode. He immideately burns
rubber, heading back towards the Dark Avian. He opens a comm-link to
Astroblast. "Yo Blast, if youre recharged, we've got something to take care
of".
